name: Schrödinger's box
description:
Audiosensitive visualization of sound piece "Dodaditty #1" by professor_h_p_p_d_generative_art.

This objkt is inspired by the paradoxical experiment of Austrian physicist Erwin Schrödinger (1887 - 1961) which is most commonly known as "Schrödinger's cat".

Click to start and stop.
Hit [space bar] to pause and resume.
